  bookPages:
  - Each step leaves a trace, without a scratch on the metal. You cannot go back
  - A catalyst, a soul. Frequency without a box.
  - "--- 1: ARTIST'S VISION ---\n\nThey gave him a form, we must give him a soul.\n\u2022
    5 Purple Flowers\n\u2022 2 Tree Shroom\nBypass our born forms."
  - "--- 2: WOOD ---\n\nThe basis of his form\n\u2022 5 Mushrooms\n\u2022 4 Tree
    Shrooms\n\nThe Moonlight has touched all, for the sun lies dormant."
  - The bubble has been popped
